Lacey Spears of Scottsville, Kentucky, was found guilty last month of second-degree murder in the death of Garnett-Paul Spears at a suburban New York hospital .
She chronicled her son Garnett's illnesses on a blog called 'Garnett's Journey' and other social media .
The New York judge who sentenced her on Wednesday said she suffers from a mental illness and said the crime was still 'unfathomable in its cruelty'